const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <>
     <Nav>
        <NavbarContainer>
            <NavLogo to='/'>
                Facial Expression

            <MobileIcon>
                <FaBars />

            <NavMenu>
                <NavItem>
                    <NavLinks to="about">About</NavLinks>
                </NavItem>
                <NavItem>
                    <NavLinks to="discover">Discover</NavLinks>
                </NavItem>
                <NavItem>
                    <NavLinks to="upload">Upload</NavLinks>
                </NavItem>
                <NavItem>
                    <NavLinks to="data">Data Analaysis</NavLinks>
                </NavItem>
            </NavMenu>
            
        </NavbarContainer>
     </Nav>
    </>
  );
}

export default Navbar
